{"tid":1783370,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識旅行社話得事嘅人？","createTime":"2019-12-14T17:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T17:52:22.000Z","uid":283675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd858d79cf34fc277b86813a60113cf7aea44c99","tid":1783370,"uid":283675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:33:13.000Z","msg":"2016年立法會旅遊界界別總票數有1322張公司票. 2018年持牌旅行社總共有1764間 (<a href=\"https://www.tar.gov.hk/text/eng/statistics/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tar.gov.hk%2Ftext%2Feng%2Fstatistics%2Findex.html&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=2e16b180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tar.gov.hk/text/eng/statistics/index.html</a>), 即係話大概有400間旅行社冇投票.<br />\n<br />\n姚思榮喺2016年嘅得票只有625張, 即係話只有大約三分之一旅行社投咗佢票.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJLVZCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJLVZCN.jpg&h=f70c46d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道我亦都明白旅遊界以及旅行社係藍到變紅, 但係我想睇下究竟有幾多黃色旅行社, 如果有足夠嘅票數, 有可能係呢個界別發揮影響作用. 即使未必能夠踢走建制, 希望至少佢唔會太過份.<br />\n<br />\n我想請問大家識唔識一啲旅行社負責人嘅同路人？我想開個群組, 數下人頭睇下夠唔夠人.<br />\n<br />\n利申：我係&ldquo;黃色&rdquo;旅行社負責人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3041080/not-your-usual-day-out-tourist-hong-kong-curious-visitors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3041080%2Fnot-your-usual-day-out-tourist-hong-kong-curious-visitors&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=15e3e75d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3041080/not-your-usual-day-out-tourist-hong-kong-curious-visitors</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你唔認識旅行社話得事嘅人, 都請你幫手推一推！"},{"pid":"59f8efabc948a37c03891b6beb2700b849a84067","tid":1783370,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3ebcef5895afdbb4639b1c9f8fe8caf7985f63","tid":1783370,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T17:52:22.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}